title: ACTREC Recruitment 2025 - Walk-in-Interview for Engineer Post
description: The Advanced Centre for Treatment Research and Education in Cancer (ACTREC) has declared the official notification for 2025. To fill up the vacancies for Engineer Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the B.E/ B.Tech. in Electrical Engineering can grab this chance and apply for these posts. Here, we include the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for the ACTREC Recruitment 2025 .
